m to the hands of the Chilean military.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIn my opinion this book is as much of a master piece as The House of Spirits, but it's also much harder to read for the violence it contains, while not explicit, it's just too real. I love Allende's styles full of regionalisms and landscape, full of hope, despite the fact that as the niece of Salvador Allende, the president assassinated by Pinochet, she has lived her life in Exile, just as Irene and Francisco.","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/74816651?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"magic-realism","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/74816651?shelf=magic-realism"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"latin-american","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/74816651?shelf=latin-american"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2210147078"},"likeCount":33,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":3,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.k02rVCA6d20lND6fCVwxlA":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.k02rVCA6d20lND6fCVwxlA","__typename":"Book"},"User:13362307":{"id":13362307,"__typename":"User","legacyId":13362307,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1466461770i/13362307._UX200_CR0,33,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":649,"viewableName":"Nikoleta","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/13362307-nikoleta","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":252},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.zBQRQg6mMU_zisaBXj1BOg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.zBQRQg6mMU_zisaBXj1BOg","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.k02rVCA6d20lND6fCVwxlA"},"creator":{"__re